(1, 'Restaurants', 'shothern spice', '10% to 15%', '40-6-22/2, Hotel Fortune Muralipark road, opp Revenue Colony Park, Beside BSNL Office,vijayawada', '0866 6633333', 'Southern Spice BLU at Tikkle Road is yet another feather in the cityâ€™s cap with its exclusive and customer friendly features like The Banquet Hall and a smart Take Away. Located in a posh environment with its ultra new ambience and luring atmosphere, we are sure to be the excellent host for you.\r\n\r\nThe Banquet Hall at Southern Spice BLU which hosts 300 people caters all the needs of business and corporate needs, seminars and get-togethers. It has the perfect ambience for conferencing set at international standards. Besides, its homely atmosphere best suits your family get-togethers, birthday functions, engagement and wedding receptions.\r\n\r\nOur Take Away at Southern Spice BLU is quite handy and smart with its ready-to-serve dishes and cuisines to lure you. You can now walk away with a variety of flavors and cuisines from our Take Away to enjoy a homely meal with your family members. We offer all varieties at a reasonable and attractive price to suit your pocket.', '../discountlogos/1restaurants2.jpg', 'DSID1', 1, '2015-06-22', '2015-06-22', 'Vijayawada', '', '', '0000-00-00', ''),
(2, 'Hotels', 'Hotel Raj Towers', '10%', 'Door No 27-14-46, Congress Office Road, Governerpet, Vijayawada - 520002', '+(91)-9177670354\r\n+(91)-866-2571311\r\nwww.hotelrajtowers.com', 'Raj Towers Vijayawada is a smart welcoming property with enchanting interiors and exteriors. It is an idyllic destination for all kinds of travelers offering an eccentric ambience for housing. The exciting accommodation with fascinating interiors offers a comfortable and delightful stay. Discover supreme relaxation and peace with gratifying and incomparable services through their experienced staff. The staff looks forward to satisfy every client with every possible way. Delectable food served in the restaurant will leave one to crave for more. \r\n\r\nLocations\r\nRaj Towers is strategically located at a renowned place at Congress Office Road with easy access to major tourist attractions like Victoria Jublilee Museum (900 m), Swarna Palace Theatre (650 m), Undavalli Caves (7.1 km), Usha Showroom (450 m), Gandhi Planetarium (3.5 km), Samarangam Chowk (2.8 km), Ratham Center (2.3 km), Siva Rama Krishna Kshetram (1.6 km), Undavalli Centre (4.9 km) and Akkanna Madanna Caves (2.8 km).\r\n\r\nVijayawada Airport - 19.3 km (Approx.)\r\nVijayawada Junction Railway Station - 3.5 km (Approx.)\r\nPandit Nehru Bus Station - 1.9 km (Approx.)\r\n\r\nFacilities\r\n\r\nRaj Towers offers an amazing range of services like multi-cuisine restaurant, bar, conference hall, indoor games and business center. The multi-cuisine restaurant serves a wide array of Indian, Continental and Chinese cuisines. There is a bar in the hotel where one can unwind with choicest of drinks. The executive lounge is well-designed for organizing meetings and conferences. A business center is well-appointed with state-of-the-art business services. Secretarial services can be provided on request. For recreational activities, there is a facility of indoor games for the guests. Foreign currency exchange counter is available from where guests can exchange their currencies. Other additional services include stand by generators, car rental, safety lockers, luggage storage and doctor on call.\r\n\r\nRooms\r\n\r\nRaj Towers offers 48 impressive rooms in three exclusive categories of Single Rooms, Double Rooms and Suites Room. The rooms are smartly designed with diminished decor and furnishings. Each room is equipped with television, mini bar, telephone and ironing board. There is an attached bathroom with the facility of running cold and hot water. Impressive room service is served to the clients.', '../discountlogos/21.jpg', 'DSID2', 1, '2015-06-23', '2015-08-21', 'Vijayawada', '', '', '0000-00-00', '10% on rooms'),
