(4, 'Auto', 'Padmaja Suzuki', '2%', 'Prabhu Nilayam, 4-1-11, Mg Road, Labbipet, Vijayawada - 520010, Near Venkateshwara Puram Post Office', '+(91)-9666662986, 9505363999', 'SUZUKI MOTORCYCLE INDIA PRIVATE LIMITED is a subsidiary of Suzuki Motor Corporation, Japan where in we are having the same manufacturing philosophy of VALUE PACKED PRODUCTS right from the inception. SMIPL will be manufacturing two wheelers best suited for the valuable Indian customers covering all segments.\r\n\r\nPlant area and production capacity\r\nWe have installed our manufacturing plant in Gurgaon (Haryana) having the annual capacity of 5,40,000 units. Total land area of the facility at Gurgaon is 37 acres out of which the present plant is constructed in an area of 10 acres of land. The remaining area is left for land development and future expansion.\r\n\r\nManaging Director\r\nMr. Masayoshi Ito', '../discountlogos/4suzuki showroom.jpg', 'DSID4', 1, '2015-06-23', '2015-06-23', 'Vijayawada', '', '', '0000-00-00', ''),
(5, 'Hotels', 'Hotel Minerva Grand', '10% to 15%', 'Mahatma Gandhi Rd, Behind Kalanikethan, Labbipet, Vijayawada, Andhra Pradesh 520010', '0866 667 8888\r\n8-2-616,Road No 11,Banjara Hills, \r\nHyderabad - 500 034, \r\nAndhra Pradesh, India. \r\nTel.: + 91 40 6719 8888 / 6612 7373\r\nFax: + 91 40 6612 7333 \r\nE-mail: resvbanjara@minervagrand.com', 'Minerva- The Roman Goddess of wisdom and commerce. \r\nThe inspiration behind Indiaâ€™s No. 1 Boutique Business Hotel in Indiaâ€™s Silicon Valley.\r\n\r\nWelcome to an oasis of tranquility, Minerva Grand, Banjara Hills. \r\nWhere state-of-the-art conveniences, discrete service, aesthetic designs and decors and fine dining experience, come together to meet your business and leisure needs. All of course brought to you with the customary hospitality that Hyderabad is known for. Minerva Grand, weâ€™ve put our heart into it.\r\n\r\nAbout Hotel Minerva Grand - Vijayawada\r\n\r\nHotel Minerva Grand, Vijayawada is a boutique business hotel centrally located and easily accessible to tourist places. It provides comfort and relaxation for business travellers, including a fine dining bar and a coffee shop. The elegant rooms present a beautiful setting to its guests to experience a pleasant time. \r\n\r\nLocation:\r\n\r\nHotel Minerva Grand is located at M.G. Road, Labbipeta. Centrally located it is in proximity to the railway station. The Madina Masjid (Approx. 0.25km) and Kanaka Durga Temple (Approx. 3km) are some of the nearby places to visit. The temple located on Indrakiladri Hill, on the banks of Krishna River is a famous Hindu temple dedicated to Goddess Kanaka Durga. Other sightseeing places include the Bhavani Island, Kondapalli Fort and Undavalli Caves.\r\n\r\nDistance from Vijayawada Junction Railway Station: Approx. 5kms\r\nDistance from Vijayawada Airport: Approx. 20kms\r\n\r\nHotel Features:\r\n\r\nThe Hotel Minerva Grand houses a reputed bar cum restaurant known as the Blue Fox, which serves multi cuisine delicacies, local flavours and delicious lip smacking beverages. The restaurant has unique mirrored architecture and a tranquil ambience. In addition, it has a coffee shop serving the best vegetarian cuisine in the area. Other basic amenities include room service, internet access, air conditioning, parking, travel desk, security and doctor-on-call. For business meeting and conferences, the hotel offers business services, meeting rooms, board room and conference suite. The banquet hall available at the hotel is beautifully furnished and decorated to hold any type of social functions.\r\n\r\nRooms:\r\n\r\nThe accommodations at Hotel Minerva Grand are spacious, airy and elegant. They offer premium rooms and imperial rooms equipped with all the modern facilities. All the rooms are air-conditioned and include telephone, bedside lamp, internet access, coloured television, in-room menu, tea/coffee maker, temperature control and massive writing desk.', '../discountlogos/5Facade.jpg', 'DSID5', 1, '2015-06-23', '2015-06-23', 'Vijayawada', '', '', '0000-00-00', ''),
(6, 'Hotels', 'Hotel Manorama', 'COMMING SOON', 'M.G. Road, Near Old Bus Stand Governorpet, Vijayawada, Andhra Pradesh 520002', '0866 257 2626', 'Hotel Manorama has 80 well appointed spacious guest rooms have both the style and substance you need for a comfortable stay.\r\nHotel Manorama has 50 Deluxe Rooms,19 Superior Rooms,10 Executive suites and a Seventh Heaven special suite.\r\n\r\nAll the rooms and suites have been newly renovated and opulently furnished with an expanded array of luxuries and most modern facilities for today''s travellers\r\n\r\nFor Enquiries & reservations  Contact +91 958 126 1234 \r\norClick here for request online', '../discountlogos/61.jpg', 'DSID6', 1, '2015-06-23', '2015-06-27', 'Vijayawada', '', '', '0000-00-00', ''),
(7, 'Hotels', 'Hotel Krishna Residency', '@10%', 'Hotel Krishna Residency, \r\nRajagopalachari Street, Opposite AMC Complex, \r\nGovernorpet, Vijayawada - 520002.', 'Phone: 0866 - 2575301, 2571571,6647251', 'PropertyHotel Krishna Residency is located in downtown of Vijayawada city in the busy Governerpet area, and it caters to the people coming to the city for shopping, dining and for business purposes. Hotel Krishna Residency is only half a kilometer from railway station and half a kilometer from bus stand, 22 kilometers from Gannavaram Airport and is at walkable from Besant road, the area which is famous for shopping in Vijayawada. Our dedicated and professional staff is committed to provide optimum customer delight and customers satisfaction. Our team has a proven track record of a successful run in the hospitality industry, and also has a vision to build a landmark hotel and to setup high standards of service. Our warm welcome makes you feel at home and courteous service ensures that you come to us you again and again. Youre just munities away from everything you need to make your trip memorable. Whatever your needs such as Board meetings, Birthday Parties, Seminars, Retirement functions, Receptions,Get Togethers, Sales Meets, Raybar is the ideal place for you. You can conduct meetings for 20 to 75 persons along with tasty and delicious food. We have different packages for your needs and our staff are more than willing to explain them to you.', '../discountlogos/DSID71.jpg', 'DSID7', 1, '2015-06-23', '2015-08-06', 'Vijayawada', '', '', '0000-00-00', '@10% on rooms. @10% on Food'),
