(32, 'Hotels', 'SEVENDAYS', 'Delux 10% Luxury @20%', 'Address:\r\nSevendays Cafe\r\n#60-9-1/a\r\nPinnamaneni Poly Clinic Road\r\nSiddhartha Nagar,\r\n6th Line,\r\nVijayawada.\r\nAddress:\r\nSeven Days Cafe(Sarada Foods),\r\n#27-6-36,\r\nPrakasam Road,\r\nGovernorpet, Vijayawada.', '0866-6662777,0866-6668777.', 'As per the accommodation each room has been exclusively designed and decorated & Luxuriously furnished for the comfort of home away from home. A classic elegance greets you from the lobby right up to the luxurious rooms and suites. This is the most centrally located hotel in the city. All the rooms are well furnished and comfortable and have been designed keeping the safety of the guest in mind, without compromising on the aesthetic appeal. Rooms are spacious well ventilated, elegantly furnished with attached bathroom. It also includes facilities like restaurant, conference and party organized. It gives you all the services mentioned below:', '../discountlogos/327.jpg', 'DSID32', 1, '2015-06-28', '2015-07-13', 'Vijayawada', 'Sevendays Banquet is the only place where you can book a function and be sure of full satisfaction of your guests. Our Banquet Halls are ideal for groups of 50 to 500 and for events ranging from Birthdays to Weddings. We take special care to make your party a memorable affair. Once you organize a function with us you will feel the warmth of our hospitality. From a simple reception to elaborate events, our services and facilities can be tailored to your requirements. Our experience will ensure that any event however large or small will exceed your highest expectations. \r\nWe have a strong base of satisfied customers who are regularly engaging us for their functions. We will be happy to go through all the options available including our extensive menu choices. Ours is the only Banquet which gives you personalized service with our highly trained team of dedicated professionals. We take extra care to see that the snacks are served hot and co