rect dial STD/ISD, Daily newspaper, Choice of fruits, In-house laundry, mini-bar\r\n\r\nThe hotel has five well-equipped banquet halls and seminar rooms . All the banquet halls and seminar rooms are well-equipped with conferencing facilities. It also includes a completely furnished and fully equipped boardroom for presentations and meetings.\r\n\r\nThe hotel offers the best of residential and non-residential banquet and conferencing facilities ideal for conferences, meetings, interviews, seminars, weddings and parties.', '2016-06-30', '20% Discount on Standard, Fortune Club&Sup.Club Rooms\r\n15% Discount on Site Rooms'),
